        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 595,
        "ruku": 533,
        "hizbQuarter": 238,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 6052,
        "text": "He who purifies it will prosper,",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 595,
        "ruku": 533,
        "hizbQuarter": 238,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 6053,
        "text": "and he who suppresses it will be ruined.",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 595,
        "ruku": 533,
        "hizbQuarter": 238,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 6054,
        "text": "In their presumptuous insolence the Thamud called the Truth a lie",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 595,
        "ruku": 533,
        "hizbQuarter": 238,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 6055,
        "text": "when their arch-criminal rose up in rage.",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 595,
        "ruku": 533,
        "hizbQuarter": 238,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 6056,
        "text": "Then Allah's Messenger warned them: “Hands off the she-camel and her drink!”",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 30,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 595,
        "ruku": 533,
        "hizbQuarter": 238,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 6057,
        "text": "But they rejected his statement as a lie and hamstrung the she-camel. For that crime their Lord rumbled down upon them, utterly razing them to the ground.",
